definition: whether or not (at the end of a phrase)

sentences.english: Sucess depends on your endeavor and capability.
sentences.chinese: 成功與否取決於你的努力和能力。

sentences.english: Successis often just the right idea away.
sentences.chinese: 勝利與否通常只是一念之差。

sentences.english: Now whether or not any of this is true, believe me, is neither here nor there.
sentences.chinese: 不管這些正確與否，相信我，關鍵不在於此。

sentences.english: The unawakened one whether does or does not do, does try.
sentences.chinese: 未覺醒的人無論行動與否，都在努力嘗試讓事情發生。

sentences.english: The success of the ship's emergency astern depends on the proper operation of the main engine.
sentences.chinese: 緊急制動成功與否，決定於主機操縱的正確程度。

sentences.english: As is well known, a nation's development is closely related to state-society relations.
sentences.chinese: 國家發展成功與否和社會之關係是休慼相關的。

sentences.english: It doesn’t matter he’s real or not, the legend will remain.
sentences.chinese: 他是真與否，都無關緊要，傳說還是會流傳下去。

sentences.english: The success will ride on our determination.
sentences.chinese: 成功與否就要看我們的決心如何了。

sentences.english: Whether you want to hear it or not, you could be allergic to your house-hold pet.
sentences.chinese: 不論你要聽與否，你可以到您家過敏貨艙寵物。

sentences.english: And whether they shall be there or not depends almost always upon non-logical, often organic conditions.
sentences.chinese: 而它們的存在與否都常常依賴於非邏輯的人腦器官。

sentences.english: Willy-nilly I didn't write blog recently.
sentences.chinese: 不管願意與否，近來我沒有寫博客。

sentences.english: Ms Royal, believe it or not, is considered a moderate.
sentences.chinese: 相信與否，羅雅爾女士被認爲是溫和派。

sentences.english: The successful development and application of a conceptual rainfall-runoff model depends mainly on how well it is calibrated.
sentences.chinese: 模型參數的識別是模糊研製與應用成功與否的關鍵。

sentences.english: You use negative words with modals to make negative clauses.
sentences.chinese: 情態動詞與否定詞連用可構成否定句。

sentences.english: The presence of adhesions did not change operative time.
sentences.chinese: 粘連的存在與否，並沒有影響手術時間。

sentences.english: It’s all about what kind of partnership you can form with them.
sentences.chinese: 收費與否取決於你與推特建立的是哪種夥伴關係。

definition: no matter what or how/regardless of whether...
whatever/no matter what (who, how etc)/regardless of/not to discuss
only natural/as it should be/certainly/of course/without doubt
after all/all in all/when all is said and done/in the final analysis
to agree (to do sth)/should/ought to/must/(legal) shall
to answer/to respond/to comply with/to deal or cope with
unrelated/having nothing to do (with sth else)
attitude (of the heart)/state of one's psyche/way of thinking/mentality
